{"sn45.40:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.40 ","sn45.40:0.2":"4. Patipattivagga ","sn45.40:0.3":"Dutiyabrahmacariyasutta ","sn45.40:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.40:1.2":"“Brahmacariyanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami, brahmacariyatthanca. ","sn45.40:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn45.40:1.4":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, brahmacariyam? ","sn45.40:1.5":"Ayameva ariyo atthangiko maggo, seyyathidam—","sn45.40:1.6":"sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.40:1.7":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmacariyam. ","sn45.40:1.8":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, brahmacariyattho? ","sn45.40:1.9":"Yo kho, bhikkhave, ragakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—","sn45.40:1.10":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmacariyattho”ti. ","sn45.40:1.11":"Dasamam. ","sn45.40:1.12":"Patipattivaggo catuttho. ","sn45.40:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn45.40:2.1":"Patipatti patipanno ca, ","sn45.40:2.2":"viraddhanca parangama; ","sn45.40:2.3":"Samannena ca dve vutta, ","sn45.40:2.4":"brahmanna apare duve; ","sn45.40:2.5":"Brahmacariyena dve vutta, ","sn45.40:2.6":"vaggo tena pavuccatiti. "}